    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>问题–<br>检测到离线安装包：shadowsocks_x.x.x.tar.gz 含非法关键词！</p><p>解决–<br>在「系统管理」- 「系统设置」里面打开「Allow SSH password login」<br>用ssh工具连接路由器 <span style="color: #519d9e; ">192.168.50.1</span><br>输入</p><pre><code class="hljs awk">sed -i <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;s/\tdetect_package/\t# detect_package/g&#x27;</span> <span class="hljs-regexp">/koolshare/</span>scripts/ks_tar_install.sh</code></pre><p>over over-</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
